I loved this very simple glazed carrot recipe. It was easy to make and just delicious; sweet, but not too sweet. My advice is to make this recipe with fresh carrots (those you find at a health food market with the green tops intact), scrub the carrots but don't peel the outer skin. Mine were very good this way.

